{"tid":1270133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果A1: 惡法未撤回 林鄭未下台 今日再上街","createTime":"2019-06-30T18:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T19:54:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7af5f2da959955702c574e791a702d2a8bca9945","tid":1270133,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/65963757_10157798216042448_8344902421385838592_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQk1xnlcUlKW34XKRIZsKAsPHzJvj9LeaNsr_cE4om7MpGcRafxtm31Ad2IgkvrhbpQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=b2a760a5ef3f736190437295e4fd79a9&amp;oe=5DC5201E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F65963757_10157798216042448_8344902421385838592_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQk1xnlcUlKW34XKRIZsKAsPHzJvj9LeaNsr_cE4om7MpGcRafxtm31Ad2IgkvrhbpQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Db2a760a5ef3f736190437295e4fd79a9%26oe%3D5DC5201E&h=d37626b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【A1頭條】香港人經歷回歸以來最傷感的6月，我們被催淚彈、胡椒噴霧熏得淚流滿面，因失去一個又一個戰友而痛不欲生；這也是最令人振奮的6月，103萬人一同為抗惡法走上街頭，200萬＋1人拒絕收貨堅持向政府怒吼，一日內成功眾籌600萬元，讓世界聽得見我們的呼喚。"},{"pid":"5be05f2aac161d4957a4d31579aec2a787e1e17d","tid":1270133,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:56:46.000Z","msg":"這個沒有人民授權的林鄭月娥政府只肯敷衍道歉、龜縮拖延，堅拒問責下台、撤回修例、撤銷暴動定性。面對冥頑不靈的政權，我們沒有放棄的餘地，也沒有放軟腳步的權利。<br />\n<br />\n走過兩次反送中大遊行的長者今日堅決再上街，為支持下一代爭取應有的權利；70後中年怒斥林鄭政府誠信破產，再一次以腳步拆穿政府謊言；80後打工仔雖然失望但未絕望，因深信走下去才看得見希望；90後女生認為「係香港人就應該行出嚟，因為唔行出嚟對唔住自己」；00後學生踏出人生第一個7.1遊行，只希望盡自己能力做好本份。<br />\n<br />\n民陣指，林鄭未下台，惡法未撤回，一日政權未回應五大訴求，香港人仍會共同進退。我們也許疲憊，但不能停下來；我們也許心痛，但拭乾眼淚便要再上路，一起走下去，一個都不能少，7.1，上街去。"},{"pid":"a00c8dd443a74e1fa3b4e88761e40d250ae18ea5","tid":1270133,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:01:54.000Z","msg":"經過尋日之後<br />\n再有藍屍挑機唔洗留手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"face333f2cb3c6510b60b4e6c5ced2752cdbabcb","tid":1270133,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8c7eb75cac10add748b34a9ebf9d30eb501ad3","tid":1270133,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:05:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ffb712e981d5a516347e8a2d608e8d6b771ae7b","tid":1270133,"uid":268224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:07:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1ed79c8e5e0ce7e03651be68af7ccddd7289e815","tid":1270133,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a00c8dd443a74e1fa3b4e88761e40d250ae18ea5","tid":1270133,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:01:54.000Z","msg":"經過尋日之後<br />\n再有藍屍挑機唔洗留手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"我對戒指用得著了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c463788e75c97fa8b8aeb68292fd2e6880bc6105","tid":1270133,"uid":127611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a00c8dd443a74e1fa3b4e88761e40d250ae18ea5","tid":1270133,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:01:54.000Z","msg":"經過尋日之後<br />\n再有藍屍挑機唔洗留手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:13:35.000Z","msg":"我地和平理性非暴力<br />\n絕對唔會主動攻擊人地<br />\n不過比人攻擊個陣一定會用合理武力去保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hk